  "description": "Walker Reynolds UNS approach — ISA-95 5-level physical hierarchy (Enterprise > Site > Area > Line > Cell). Flat, clean and self-describing. No functional branch prefixes. Single source of truth: every signal at exactly one physical topic. Report-by-exception. JSON payload with timestamp, value, unit, quality, source. Based on iiot.university / virtualfactory.online UNS philosophy.",
